Bar Nancy.
Created with the dream of making a great neighborhood bar. Nancy, espouses Revolutionary Zeal in her no-nonsense approach to hospitality.

Facts
The Courtyard is a place where passengers disembark to relax and unwind in a zen tiki experience.
The port hole that now leads travelers to The Courtyard in Nancy’s back patio once was part of a respectable sailing vessel.
Nancy loves live music just as much as she loves her cocktails.
Nancy is parked on Calle Ocho, Little Havana
Nancy is made up of some great people..

A Proper Place to
Drink
Expertly Crafted
Drinks
&
Cocktails
Nancy is a nautically themed American Craft Cocktail Bar located on Calle Ocho in Little Havana. The cocktail bar takes its inspiration from the American Revolutionary sailing vessel, Nancy. Nancy carried ammunition and spirits during the American Revolutionary War.
The Nancy creed “Carpe Noctem, ”or “Seize the Night” , promises good times through an authentic & inspired bar experience.
